# NPM Ignore - Final Pruning

# 1. Dev & Meta garbage
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
**/.github/
**/.husky/
**/.vscode/
**/.DS_Store
package-lock.json
*.tgz
*.log
tests/
**/__tests__/

# 2. Binary & Media Purge (Recursive across all whitelisted folders)
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.webp
**/*.mov
**/*.mp4
**/*.wasm
**/*.heapsnapshot
**/*.gz
**/*.node
**/*.zip
**/*.tar.gz

# 3. Exceptions for brand assets (Whitelisted in package.json anyway, but being safe)
!assets/logo.png
!assets/banner.png

# 4. Framework specific garbage
.ai-core/plugins/
.ai-core/external/
.ai-core/backups/
.ai-core/memory.db
.ai-core/cache/
